&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; 3+ years in a data-centric role (Analytics, Data Engineering, or BI)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Acumen:&lt;/strong&gt; Experience with solving real-world problems with data and translating data insights into outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
